00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:36,120
So the first principle

76
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:39,480
you have to understand within yourself,

77
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:42,920
that you should be able to create

78
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:46,680
a new personality in a person.

79
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:55,280
So how do we do it?

80
00:06:55,480 --> 00:07:00,400
Of course you have got powers to raise the Kundalini,

81
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:06,800
you have got powers to cure people,

