you have got powers to talk big or talk small.

83
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:16,480
Despite all that,

84
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:20,960
if you cannot create a new personality

85
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:24,680
out of the persons with whom you are dealing,

86
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:28,800
then you are not a guru.

87
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,640
And the new personality has to be

88
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:36,640
a special personality of very unique

89
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:43,520
combination of compassion and dynamism.

90
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:49,840
So it is important

91
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:56,640
that in your creativity

92
00:07:56,840 --> 00:08:04,440
you have to use the energy of compassion.

93
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:08,680
You can only mold people through compassion

94
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:11,920
and never through anger,

95
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:15,080
never through suppression,

96
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:17,960
never through showing off

97
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:22,160
your powers of gurudom.

98
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:28,640
Unless and until you handle the situation

99
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:33,080
and the personality very carefully,

100
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:37,600
showing all the respect,

101
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:41,160
showing all the concern

102
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:44,120
and all the love

103
