00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:07,000
then your Guru Principle is wasted.

133
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:11,680
It is the effort of Sahaja Yoga that is wasted,

134
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:16,120
and your Guru's job is also wasted.

135
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:28,400
Minimum of minimum, first the attention has to be pure.

136
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:34,160
But pure attention doesn't mean harshness,

137
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:37,080
it doesn't mean asceticism,

138
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:39,880
it doesn't mean disciplining your eyes

139
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:44,440
like a blinkers of horse,

140
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:47,040
but in all freedom

141
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:52,440
your attention to be concentrated.

142
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:56,280
Where do we pay our attention the most?

143
00:11:56,480 --> 00:12:01,680
If we are honest we can think on human level

144
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:05,440
we pay our attention to our children,

145
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:10,080
to our wife, to our husbands, to our family,

146
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:16,520
the relationships which are with love.

147
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:22,520
So when your attention

148
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:26,920
has got

149
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:32,640
the compassion

150
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:37,920
and the love for another person,

151
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:44,160
then only you can work out the realization of others.

152
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:48,080
If you have to work out the realization of others,

153
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:53,560
it has to be an intense love

154
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:57,480
for another person.

155
00:12:57,720 --> 00:13:01,680
If you don't have that intensity,

156
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:05,280
you are just moving your hands raising the kundalini

157
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:09,360
because your Mother has given you powers, and it's finished

158
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:13,200
That intensity of love

159
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:17,200
can only give you success

160
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:19,520
with your pure attention,

161
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:25,840
and I think the pure attention can only love.

162
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:28,560
Impure attention cannot love,

163
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:33,600
because all impure attention is self-oriented,

164
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:36,360
I-oriented.

165
00:13:36,560 --> 00:13:42,480
They are not "self" in the sense "spiritual-oriented."

166
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:50,320
But the idea that spirituality is love,

167
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:54,680
it seems to be a new idea for many people.

168
00:13:55,480 --> 00:14:00,360
They think spirituality means a person who is just

169
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:05,240
absolutely dry like a beanstalk

170
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:07,680
and

171
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:12,240
nobody can go near that person,

172
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:15,480
nobody can communicate

173
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:22,560
with such a person because that person is "too pure."

174
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:27,320
If the soap cannot cleanse your body,

175
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:31,200
