176
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:36,480
If the soap is afraid to come near you,

177
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:41,720
then it's better not to be called as soap.

178
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:46,120
So we come to the point

179
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:53,480
that the creativity, if it is our aim, lakshya,

180
00:14:53,680 --> 00:14:58,840
for that the attention we should purify,

181
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:07,840
and to be purified with love, with compassion.

182
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:14,280
And the same attention when it is filled with love and comp

183
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:18,920
it gives you dynamism, it gives you strength,

184
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:24,040
it's untiring zeal you get.

185
00:15:25,920 --> 00:15:32,200
And the joy of seeing your reflection into another person

186
00:15:32,880 --> 00:15:35,320
is very beautiful.

187
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:38,640
No words can describe it.

188
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:42,760
Actually when you give realization to another person,

189
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:47,320
what you try to see is your image in that person,

190
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:50,760
as if out of an ordinary glass

191
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:54,200
you are making it into a beautiful mirror

192
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:57,520
and then you want to see that.

193
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:00,600
That is how you create,

194
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:05,920
you create your own reflections and

195
00:16:07,040 --> 00:16:11,960
through the cleansing of the reflectors,

196
00:16:12,640 --> 00:16:17,920
once you understand that without creativity

197
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:21,440
this Guru Puja is useless for you.

198
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:26,720
If you just live for yourself, or your family,

199
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:32,160
for your husband or just for an ashram,

200
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:34,920
then you have not expanded at all,

201
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:40,760
you have not done any duty towards your Guru.

202
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:49,640
Of course as soon as you take to this principle

203
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:52,400
you develop so many qualities within you.

204
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:56,280
The first you develop is wisdom,

205
00:16:57,520 --> 00:17:02,080
because you realize where you are going wrong,

206
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:07,360
why this is not working out, why there's a problem,

207
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:11,080
why your creativity doesn't act.

208
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:16,600
It becomes evident to you, obvious to you

209
00:17:16,840 --> 00:17:19,520
and you start learning;

210
00:17:20,600 --> 00:17:24,400
and wisdom comes to you, and you understand.

211
00:17:24,600 --> 00:17:28,200
Wisdom is when you realize your mistakes

212
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:31,200
and rectify them,

213
00:17:31,760 --> 00:17:36,080
and with that you develop the balance,

214
00:17:36,320 --> 00:17:38,840
the understanding

215
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:43,520
how to deal with another personality.

216
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:48,600
I always tell the story of a car,

217
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:53,680
that there's an accelerator and also there's a brake.

218
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:58,200
You have to use first both of them without understanding why

219
00:17:58,400 --> 00:18:00,800
still you are not a guru,

220
00:18:01,800 --> 00:18:03,840
you are not even a driver.

221
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:07,640
Then when you know then you automatically drive;

222
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:12,760
then you are a driver, but still the master is sitting behind

223
00:18:13,360 --> 00:18:16,040
So now you have to become the master,

224
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:20,240
and when you become the master you can balance the vehicle

225
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:26,880
and you can see the driver, accelerator and also the brake.

226
00:18:27,080 --> 00:18:32,920
And you can manage it just in a very simple manner.

227
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:39,160
So this Guru Principle is limited,

228
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:44,200
and goes on increasing its limitations

229
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:50,200
like the horizon.

230
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:55,680
As you start growing into more creativity,

231
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:59,520
the more people you create.

232
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:05,160
And the central point of this one is the Nabhi,

233
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:08,640
is the center which

234
00:19:08,840 --> 00:19:12,320
like a big pivotal point

235
00:19:12,520 --> 00:19:17,640
on which the whole of this movement takes place.

236
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:22,440
Nabhi Chakra as you know,

237
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:27,040
you get it from your mother to begin with.

238
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:31,120
So a guru has to be the mother,

239
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:34,600
he must have the qualities of the mother

240
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:39,480
not the modern mothers, but in the real sense of the word.

241
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,520
That is,

242
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:47,240
a guru has to love her children

243
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:52,360
and has to have strength and courage

244
00:19:52,560 --> 00:19:55,680
to correct her children.

245
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:59,760
And the earnest desire should be

246
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:02,800
to put the children onto proper lines

247
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:06,840
to guide them and to help them to rise.

248
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:12,440
So the first nourishment comes to us

249
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:17,160
even when we are in the womb of the mother,

250
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:20,800
through the mother; and so

251
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:25,040
you are the mother though you may be a man or a woman,

252
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:29,400
but in quality you are the mother.

253
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:34,080
And whatever you think or whatever you do

254
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:38,840
has an effect on the child.

255
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:42,920
The way you behave, the way you talk,

256
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:47,000
the way you live, everything has a bearing

257
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:51,560
on the development of the child.

258
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:54,440
In the same way when,

259
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:58,600
supposing a Sahaja yogi who is trying to give realization

260
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:04,680
is a hypocritical person, if he's a wrong type of a person,

261
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:08,800
if he does not respect his own Guru,

262
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:14,000
the children behave the same manner

263
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:17,720
and they take to wrong things much faster,

264
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:20,640
they see to wrong things first.

265
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:25,840
So you have to be perfect in your behavior

266
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:29,440
towards your own Guru,

267
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:34,400
you have to respect your own Guru in a full way.

268
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:38,160
Complete surrender to your own Guru is important;

269
00:21:38,360 --> 00:21:42,360
then they will see how you have treated your own Guru,

270
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:46,000
and that is how they will treat you.

271
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:50,440
If you don't treat your Guru with that respect,

272
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:53,160
with that understanding,

273
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:55,360
with that surrendering,

274
00:21:55,560 --> 00:21:59,600
then don't expect your children

275
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:05,160
or the people whom you are guiding are going to respect you

276
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:09,640
So this Guru Principle within us has to be

277
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:14,600
like a great sage or a great seer,

278
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:19,920
who is above the normal mundane people

279
00:22:20,120 --> 00:22:24,320
and sees the things in a proper perspective,

280
00:22:24,800 --> 00:22:28,080
and delivers

281
00:22:28,360 --> 00:22:32,080
a proper understanding

282
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:36,320
of all this perspective he sees,

283
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:38,200
to his disciples,

284
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:43,320
doesn't give them distorted or wrong ideas.

285
00:22:47,120 --> 00:22:54,360
Now one may say that, "Mother, how is it, that the love

286
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:59,400
we can express and also tell them the truth?"

287
00:23:00,520 --> 00:23:07,800
You have to look after the benevolence -- hitha.

288
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:14,200
You have to look after the benevolence of your disciple.

289
00:23:14,320 --> 00:23:16,560
It may appear that

290
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:21,240
he may not like what you are telling that person today,

291
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:24,880
but a day will come when he will think

292
00:23:25,080 --> 00:23:28,240
"Thank God your Guru has corrected you

293
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:31,160
and has put you on the right path."

294
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:36,320
If the goal of the disciple is not to ascend,

295
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:41,480
is just to be there for some sort of a purpose,

296
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:45,880
then it's better not to have such disciples.

297
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:48,880
Not to have anyone of this kind

298
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:54,000
who are not there for their own ascent,

299
00:23:54,240 --> 00:24:01,800
but for other gains, which are absolutely of no avail.

300
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:13,160
This question arises sometimes, how to love?

301
00:24:13,320 --> 00:24:16,240
It's a very funny question

302
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:20,400
that we don't know how to love human beings.

303
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:25,160
We can love our things, we can love our useless things,

304
00:24:25,320 --> 00:24:31,080
we can love some sort of a beautiful scenery

305
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:33,160
because it gives us joy.

306
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:36,240
We can love some

307
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:39,720
nice restaurant because you can get good food there,

308
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:44,560
or some sort of a thing which is of a very baser nature.

309
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:51,160
But love for love's sake is this,

310
00:24:51,320 --> 00:24:58,160
that when you really love for love's sake,

311
00:24:58,320 --> 00:25:01,160
then you try to put

312
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:06,960
or implant that love into somebody else,

313
00:25:07,320 --> 00:25:14,080
that you make another person as loveable as you are.

314
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:19,560
So the whole system becomes different if you understand

315
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:24,080
that we have to base all our progress,

316
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:28,880
all our love, all our movements, all our behavior,

317
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:32,480
all our understanding on love.

318
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:36,080
Otherwise your Guru Principl is extremely weak,

319
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:40,160
and after some time you will find you are just standing

320
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:44,800
out of the shores of Sahaja Yoga.

321
00:25:48,320 --> 00:25:53,880
Anybody who is attached or biased and has conditionings

322
00:25:54,080 --> 00:25:57,400
cannot become a guru, cannot;

323
00:25:57,600 --> 00:26:00,560
because even if he becomes, so-called,

324
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:04,960
all those things will be reflected in that person.

325
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:09,960
Or say if he is very full of ego, thinks no end of himself

326
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:13,960
and thinks that, "I am a great guru,"

327
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:17,160
that ego also would be expressed.

328
00:26:17,320 --> 00:26:20,960
Supposing such a guru talks too much,

329
00:26:21,880 --> 00:26:27,160
also they find the disciple the same style.

330
00:26:27,320 --> 00:26:32,160
If he is a quiet type, you find the disciple the same style

331
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:36,640
So we reach a conclusion that first we must develop

332
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:40,400
our own Guru Principle.

333
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:48,960
If we cannot develop that, it is no use doing any Guru Puja

334
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:54,640
because it is just temporary, it's not going to help you much,

335
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:59,640
unless and until you really decide

336
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:05,160
that you are going to nourish

337
00:27:05,400 --> 00:27:10,720
and develop and establish your Guru Principle.

338
00:27:12,320 --> 00:27:16,480
So today when you are worshipping Me as the Guru,

339
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:19,320
you must know that any amount of My talking,

340
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:25,000
any amount of My giving you blessings or anything

341
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:28,320
is not going to work out, nless and until

342
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:35,400
we really develop our own Guru Principle, and the depth.

343
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:39,800
Because a guru

344
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:46,000
makes his disciple cross the Bhavasagara,

345
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:49,000
he's like the boat

346
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:55,400
who takes his disciples and crosses

347
00:27:56,400 --> 00:28:02,240
with love and with proper direction.

348
00:28:03,080 --> 00:28:06,640
That has to be with all of you.

349
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:09,960
As it is you are all realized souls

350
00:28:10,160 --> 00:28:13,080
and as I have told you, you are all angels.

351
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:16,960
But if you do not establish your Guru Principle,

352
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:22,800
you know of angels how they have fallen down and gone forever.

353
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:27,480
So be careful: it's easy to be an angel

354
00:28:27,680 --> 00:28:30,480
but difficult to maintain it.

355
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:34,800
It is difficult to be the Gods and Goddesses,

356
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:38,560
but easy to maintain it.

357
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:47,640
So all of you are here. I'm very happy to see

358
00:28:47,960 --> 00:28:51,720
that you have come to worship Me as your Guru.

359
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:56,880
And I would expect that My children

360
00:28:57,080 --> 00:29:00,720
are after My own image.

361
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:04,640
That My image should be such that My children

362
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:09,080
should feel that oneness with My image,

363
00:29:09,320 --> 00:29:14,240
and I should be a proud Mother of so many children

364
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:17,480
who have come from so many countries.

365
00:29:17,720 --> 00:29:21,160
May God bless you all.

366
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:36,080
Now with so many people here, so many children here,

367
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:42,240
we can have all the children just to wash My feet,

368
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:45,160
and after that we'll need some girls

369
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:49,160
who are above sixteen years

370
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:53,640
to twenty-one years, we can say.

371
00:29:55,160 --> 00:29:58,560
And then some ladies

372
00:29:58,720 --> 00:30:02,080
for the purpose of

373
00:30:05,320 --> 00:30:09,720
worshipping Shakti, the Goddess.

374
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:14,160
Without the Shakti nothing can be done.

375
00:30:15,080 --> 00:30:21,640
So first the children have to come up just to wash the feet

376
00:30:45,560 --> 00:30:50,400
And I hope the world leaders will be here also.

377
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:55,400
They are in the image of gurus now.

378
00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:59,160
And the leaders have to be something special.

379
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:01,160
You are not a leader

380
00:31:01,320 --> 00:31:06,800
if you are such an ordinary, mundane type of a person.

381
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:46,880
Now, where are the musicians?

382
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:55,560
Where are the musicians?

383
00:31:55,800 --> 00:31:57,160
All right.

384
00:31:57,320 --> 00:32:01,880
So you have to first say the Atharva Sheersha,

385
00:32:02,080 --> 00:32:06,800
and then you have to sing the Ganesha Stuthi,

386
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:11,240
or maybe any other thing that you know of Ganesha.

